Name: Bunny adventure
About the game: Bunny adventure is fun, casual platformer for all ages. Complete 6 stages of platforming, find all collectibles and secrets and get highest score! Bunny is lost in the woods and now he needs to find a way to his island, wher his girlfriend bunny awaits him! In his adventure he will encounter all sorts of enemies, challenges and interesting palces! Features: 1) Colorful and beautiful graphics 2) Fun gameplay 3) 6 interesting levels 4) Secret treasures to find!
